      "contentBlocks": [
        "Mechanical Engineering applies the principles of science and mathematics to the design of machinery and equipment used in the rapidly evolving areas of transportation, manufacturing and energy conversion. Balancing fundamentals, analytical methods, and design applications, the program prepares graduates for long-term engineering careers.",
        "The Mechanical Engineering Department offers the following degrees:",
        "Bachelor of Science (BS) Degree in Mechanical Engineering",
        "Master of Science (MS) Degree in Mechanical Engineering",
